### Contract 3 — `ScoringResult` (output of M3, input to M4)

```python
scoring_result = {
    "total_score": 54,                 # out of 100
    "decision": "LEND WITH CONDITIONS",  # LEND / LEND WITH CONDITIONS / REJECT
    "components": {
        "financial_health":  22,       # max 35
        "gst_compliance":    12,       # max 20
        "promoter_quality":   9,       # max 20
        "external_intel":     8,       # max 15
        "officer_override":   3,       # max 10 (entered via UI)
    },
    "loan_terms": {
        "requested_cr": 15.0,
        "recommended_cr": 8.0,
        "interest_rate_pct": 11.5,     # base + risk premium
        "tenure_months": 36,
        "conditions": ["Review in 6 months", "Quarterly GST audit required"],
    },
    "explanation_narrative": (
        "Apex Textiles Pvt Ltd presents a MEDIUM-HIGH risk profile. "
        "The DSCR of 0.89 falls below the RBI threshold of 1.25 (Financial Health: -13 pts). "
        "An 18.2% GST mismatch signals potential ITC discrepancy (GST: -8 pts). "
        "NCLT litigation, though dismissed, indicates promoter risk (-15 pts). "
        "Recommend reduced sanction of ₹8 Cr at prime+2.5% with 6-month review."
    ),
    "shap_contributions": {            # for the waterfall chart
        "dscr":              -13,
        "gst_mismatch":       -8,
        "litigation":        -15,
        "avg_bank_balance":   +7,
        "news_sentiment":     -4,
    },
    "ews_signals": [
        {"level": 2, "label": "Special Mention", "reason": "GST mismatch > 15% — potential ITC fraud"},
        {"level": 1, "label": "Watch",           "reason": "Litigation history found — NCLT case"},
    ],
    "cam_path": "output/Apex_Textiles_CAM.docx",
}
```

