## 📅 10-Day Sprint Calendar

```
Day  | M1 (Docs)          | M2 (Research)       | M3 (Scoring)        | M4 (Frontend)
-----|---------------------|---------------------|---------------------|------------------
 1   | Setup + pdfplumber  | Setup + Tavily acct | Design scorecard    | Setup Streamlit
 2   | FinancialExtractor  | MCA Scraper         | ScorecardModel      | Upload + Financial panel
 3   | GSTValidator        | ECourtSearcher      | LoanCalculator      | GST + Research panel
 4   | BankParser          | NewsAggregator      | ExplainabilityEng   | Score dashboard
 5   | ✅ INTEGRATION 1    | ✅ INTEGRATION 1    | ✅ INTEGRATION 1    | ✅ Wire pipelines
 6   | Polish + confidence | Cache + demo mode   | CAM Generator       | EWS panel
 7   | Buffer / QA         | Buffer / QA         | MLflow setup        | CSS polish
 8   | ✅ INTEGRATION 2    | ✅ INTEGRATION 2    | ✅ INTEGRATION 2    | ✅ Full end-to-end
 9   | Demo rehearsal      | Demo rehearsal      | Presentation deck   | Demo video backup
10   | SUBMISSION DAY      | SUBMISSION DAY      | SUBMISSION DAY      | SUBMISSION DAY
```

### Integration Day 5 — Goal
- M1 drops `modules/document_intelligence/mock_data.py` into shared repo ✅
- M2 drops `modules/research_agent/mock_data.py` into repo ✅
- M3 runs scoring on M1 + M2 mock data, generates a CAM doc ✅
- M4 loads all three mock JSONs into the UI — full flow visible on Day 5 ✅

### Integration Day 8 — Goal
- Replace ALL mock calls with real pipeline calls in `app.py`
- Full live demo flow: upload PDFs → process → score → CAM download
- Both demo companies pre-cached: **Apex Textiles (REJECT)** + one healthy company **(LEND)**

