## 🔧 Shared Repository Setup

```
intelli-credit/                    ← GitHub repo root
  app.py                           ← M4
  requirements.txt                 ← all libs merged
  .env                             ← API keys (Gemini, Tavily, NewsAPI) — NEVER commit
  .env.example                     ← template to share safely
  demo_data/                       ← mock JSONs all teams can use
  output/                          ← generated CAM docs land here
  modules/
    document_intelligence/         ← M1
    research_agent/                ← M2
    scoring/                       ← M3
  presentation/
    slides/
    architecture_diagram.png
```

**Branch strategy:** Each person works on `feature/<name>` branch. Merge to `main` only on Integration Days.

---

## 🚦 When You Are Blocked

| Situation | Solution |
|-----------|----------|
| M1 not ready → M3 is blocked | Use `mock_data.py` — it's guaranteed to exist by Day 5 |
| M2 scraper fails | Set `demo_mode=True` — returns pre-cached JSON |
| M3 CAM generator slow | M4 shows a placeholder download button — wire it on Day 8 |
| Any API quota hit | Gemini free tier: 1,500 req/day. Tavily: 1,000/month free tier |

